title: Gołębiów, Grójec County
data: Gołębiów [ɡɔˈwɛmbjuf] is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Jasieniec, within Grójec County, Masovian Voivodeship, in east-central Poland.[1] It lies approximately 15 kilometres (9 mi) east of Grójec and 44 km (27 mi) south of Warsaw.
